{"tid":1130525,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"巴膠疑預好角度　封路拍攝　巴士埋站慘被塞住","createTime":"2019-04-29T06:08:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T06:08:18.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"0c30cde911ddd6e298a0e6d25c414adc81047236","tid":1130525,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T06:08:18.000Z","msg":"巴士迷疑預好角度 封路拍攝 巴士埋站慘被塞住<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2L5X0D0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2L5X0D0&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9YDkkQuUBcdRTUhzZaMUkok%3D&h=151ef2eb\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2L5X0D0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190429/photo/bkn-20190429123132023-0429_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190429125247\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190429%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190429123132023-0429_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190429125247&h=f8a38c9a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為咗影巴士，可以去到幾盡？<br />\n<br />\n據Facebook群組「巴士的事討論區」的貼文表示，周日（28日）下午1時40分，有幾名手持相機的男子，站在西九龍站巴士總站附近的安全島，疑在拍攝路經的巴士。<br />\n<br />\n有目擊者批評，他們疑為取得較佳的拍攝角度，擅自將雪糕筒搬出馬路左線，結果阻礙巴士駛入巴士總站。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190429/photo/bkn-20190429123132023-0429_00822_001_02p.jpg?20190429125247\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190429%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190429123132023-0429_00822_001_02p.jpg%3F20190429125247&h=a0bd25b2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有人把雪糕筒放置於馬路左線。（互聯網）"}]}